secrets - Secret Management

USAGE:
    secrets <action> [options]

DESCRIPTION:
    Manage secrets and passwords. Supports getting, finding, putting,
    deleting, and generating secrets.

ACTIONS:
    get <secret-key>
        Get secret value (placed on clipboard by default)
        
        Options:
        -stdout       Output to stdout instead of clipboard
        -wifi         Generate WiFi QR code (requires secret structure)
        -qrcode       Generate QR code for secret

    find <pattern1> [pattern2...]
        Find secrets matching patterns

    value-grep <secret-value>
        Search for specific secret value (pass only)

    put <secret-key>
        Add/update secret (prompts for value)

    delete <secret-key>
        Delete a secret

    generate
        Generate new password
        
        Options:
        -conf-generate-capitalize=0      Don't capitalize
        -conf-generate-numerals=0        Don't include numerals  
        -conf-password-length=10         Generate 10 character password

CONFIGURATION:
    Options must precede action

EXAMPLES:
    secrets get api-key
    secrets get wifi-network/upstairs -wifi
    secrets find database
    secrets put new-password
    secrets delete old-key
    secrets generate -conf-password-length=16
